	<ol class="children">
	<li class="comment odd alt depth-2 comment-item">
		<article id="comment-105104" class="comment-block">
			<header class="comment-header">
				<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/4661d291711d168be8d9b33c1b73f885?s=44&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' />				<cite class="comment-author">Robert Marchenoir</cite>
				<a class="comment-permalink" href="http://h16free.com/2013/03/10/21712-and-speaking-about-instruction/comment-page-1#comment-105104" title="16 h 04 min"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2013-03-11T16:04:59+00:00">11 mars 2013, 16 h 04 min</time></a>			</header>

			
			<div class="comment-content comment">
				<p>C&rsquo;est possible, le Gnôme ? Il n&rsquo;y a pas de limite d&rsquo;âge ?</p>
			</div>
			<div class="comment-action">
				<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2013/03/10/21712-and-speaking-about-instruction?replytocom=105104#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-105104", "105104", "respond", "21712")'>Répondre</a>							</div>
